    "Our ablations show that neither extreme is ideal: relying only on short-form or only on long-form data is suboptimal.",
    "Removing long-form data substantially degrades performance on all four long-form datasets.",
    "Conversely, removing short-form data leaves HealthBench, ResearchQA, and DRB largely unchanged, but noticeably reduces performance on 2Wiki and SQAv2.",
